name: Ladybug Love Party Kit-Printable PDF File
description:
********************************************* This listing is for PDF files that will be sent to your email address. The purchased, high resolution PDF files, will NOT be shipped to your home. All files are formatted to 8.5" x 11" letterhead sized sheets AND THIS FILE IS NOT EDITABLE. Colors may vary slightly from above depending on your monitor and printer used. ********************************************* This adorable party kit includes templates for making: -5 x 7 inch invitations with "RSVP" line / Invitations with "Regrets to" line versions -4.25 x 5.75 inch invitations with "RSVP" line / Invitations with "Regrets to" line versions -4.25 x 5.75 inch Thank you cards -One 4.5 " x 6" envelope template for thank you cards and smaller invite -2 inch circle tags (perfect as cupcake toppers, tags, decorating cups, etc. -3 Party hat designs -4 patterned sheets -Cutouts of ladybug and flowers -Flag (triangle) shaped garlands -2 goodie bag cards designs -3 goodie bag cards (flag style) -Letterhead sign with "Happy Birthday" on it -Horizontal tags--perfect for lollipop tags, hang tags, etc. -Table mat -Place holder cards -2 Cupcake wrapper designs -Coloring sheet -Purses - Various triangle shaped banners -"Happy Birthday" banner -"PARTY" banner -Various flag toppers -Mini tags (used as cupcake toppers above) -Napkin and water bottle wrappers -4 inch circles -Instructions on how to make flower pot centerpiece -Templates for making paper flower -3 large 11 x 17 inches posters ********************************************* T E R M S • O F • U S E ********************************************* These files are password-protected-you will NOT be able to alter contents inside files in Photoshop or other programs. You will only be able to open the PDF files in Adobe Acrobat or other PDF reading software for UNLIMITED printing for your own PERSONAL use. The use of these images for commercial use, profitability, re-selling, mass production, altering for your own use, or re-selling of the finished product as shown on photos above is strictly prohibited. You also MAY NOT place these images as part of websites, logos, or similar mediums OR scan the designs and use them digitally or offer any printables with these images. All artwork is © PaperGlitter. The copyright is not transferable with the sale of any PDF file and the buyer is not entitled to reproduction rights.You may only purchase the files IF YOU AGREE with the above terms of use. Thank you for your support. Oh--one last thing---no sharing of these files please---these files were made with lots of hard work and love ^_^ PaperGlitter.com.
**************************************** M A T E R I A L S • N E E D E D **************************************** • Cardstock and regular papers in letterhead sizes (label paper if making any of the tags as stickers) • Printer to print PDF file • Purchased PDF file • A7 envelope (5.25 x 7.25 inches) if making 5 x 7 invitations • Scissors, glue stick or glue, stapler with staples (for hats) double sided tape and regular tape • Lollipop sticks if making cupcake toppers • String (if hanging garlands) • Burnisher of Bone Folder for scoring • Elastic string or ribbons for hats • Paper bags or clear candy bags for making goodie bags as shown above • Optional: But highly recommended a 2 inch circle puncher for cutting circle tags for making cupcake toppers **************************************** S O F T W A R E • N E E D E D **************************************** Please make sure you have a PDF reader or Adobe Acrobat software installed for reading your purchased PDF files. If you don't have the appropriate software, you can download Adobe Acrobat for free at: www.adobe.com
